data.description: Adorable farmhouse with 4 bedrooms 2.5 bathrooms, a 5 car garage, and a pole barn on 2.84 gated acres. If you have been dreaming ofpeace and quiet while still having easy access to shopping, beaches, and the interstate, then you have found your match! The house issituated perfectly to allow distance from the road while leaving ample space to utilize the back field for agriculture. Beautiful hardwoodfloors run throughout the main house and tile is in the wet areas and sunroom. The floor plan, kitchen and bathrooms are modern whilestill maintaining the farmhouse charm. Schedule your showing today to see how lovely this home truly is.
